    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Mr. and Mrs. Fred Drebis of Pa\nlouise Falls, Wash, are in the city\nvisiting with friends. Mr.. Drebis\nis superintendent of the demonstra-\nton farm of the Palouse Irrigation\nand Power company, in the Wash.\ntucna valley. and while in the city\nWill purchase large amount of\nsupplies to be used in the construc-\nton of one of the large company\nbitches and fumes. Mr.. Drebis\nspent Is years in the Wenatchee\nvalley and helped build that valley\nup, but thinks the Washtucna val\nley will lead all the other valleys\nin the state for gardening or fruit\ngrowing."
    }
  ]
